# Telegram bot setup:
# 1. Open Telegram, search for @BotFather
# 2. Send /newbot and follow the prompts — copy the token it gives you
# 3. Search for your new bot and send it any message
# 4. Visit https://api.telegram.org/bot<YOUR_TOKEN>/getUpdates in a browser
# 5. Find "chat":{"id": <number>} in the response — that's your CHAT_ID
